  "text": "MCDM enhances a DM's ability to examine trade-offs between options and assess their influences on different stakeholders [CITATION_1] . There are several, usually inconsistent, targets linked to the selection of programs/projects for inclusion in a portfolio; for instance, are financial targets more important than political ones, and if so, to exactly what degree? In a MCDM's closing stage, the ideal option is that which offers an appropriate cross-section of trade-offs among variables [CITATION_2] .",
